37
00:01:36,890 --> 00:01:38,440
♪May I live and die
with the sun♪

38
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:41,180
=Guardians of the Dafeng=

39
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:44,140
=Episode 12=

40
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:45,750
Is there anything else?

41
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,600
If not, let's call it a day.

42
00:01:47,610 --> 00:01:49,550
I have bandits to kill
in the mountains tomorrow.

43
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:50,740
(No. 2, No. 3)
No, 3,

44
00:01:50,750 --> 00:01:52,190
we've been here for so long.

45
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:53,640
May I know

46
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:54,960
your name?

47
00:01:56,910 --> 00:01:57,800
I go

48
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,310
by this name only.

49
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:00,640
It's

50
00:02:00,830 --> 00:02:02,190
Chen Jinnan!

51
00:02:04,700 --> 00:02:07,260
(Realm Sect: Core Members, Mirror Holders)

52
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:10,110
Did you draw this table?

53
00:02:10,430 --> 00:02:11,270
Yes.

54
00:02:11,710 --> 00:02:13,200
It looks creative.

55
00:02:15,830 --> 00:02:16,800
Tell me about it.

56
00:02:18,430 --> 00:02:19,320
As you can see,

57
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,990
the Realm Sect holds nine core members.

58
00:02:21,990 --> 00:02:24,200
They're holders of the Jade Mirrors, too,

59
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:26,430
and sorted by their mirror numbers.

60
00:02:26,550 --> 00:02:28,430
No. 1 is in the capital

61
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,360
with powerful figures behind, I believe.

62
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,710
He's likely to work for the court.

63
00:02:33,150 --> 00:02:34,390
No. 6 seems

64
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:35,920
straightforward

65
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:37,080
and easygoing.

66
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:39,390
We can use him to our advantage.

67
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:40,710
As for No. 3,

68
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,040
he's charming,

69
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,870
fun to hang out with,

70
00:02:43,870 --> 00:02:44,800
faithful,

71
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,830
and upright.

72
00:02:45,830 --> 00:02:47,760
Identity: Copper Gong Guardian.

73
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:48,920
Yes, that's me.

74
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:56,430
As for No. 5, No. 7, No. 8,

75
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,670
we haven't talked.

76
00:02:57,670 --> 00:02:58,920
It's hard to say.

77
00:02:59,830 --> 00:03:01,080
No. 2, Li Miaozhen,

78
00:03:01,390 --> 00:03:02,520
is in Yunzhou,

79
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,710
devoted to killing bandits.

80
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:05,670
People call her Winged Woman.

81
00:03:06,270 --> 00:03:07,760
No. 4, Chu Yuanzhen, is

82
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:09,550
the Chief Disciple of the Treasure Sect.

83
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:11,640
Those two have been hostile

84
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:13,320
to each other for a long time.

85
00:03:17,110 --> 00:03:18,320
He's also

86
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,390
the Saint of Men.

87
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:23,520
Do you know him, Lord Wei?

88
00:03:23,990 --> 00:03:26,640
Li Miaozhen must be the Saintess of Heaven.

89
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:28,320
Heaven and Men

90
00:03:28,670 --> 00:03:29,870
have never ceased fighting.

91
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,640
Those two will battle someday.

92
00:03:36,150 --> 00:03:38,390
Have you found out why Jinlian

93
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,320
founded the Realm Sect?

94
00:03:42,550 --> 00:03:43,550
He said after the Head

95
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:45,920
of Earth was demonized,

96
00:03:46,390 --> 00:03:48,080
he founded the Realm Sect.

97
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,040
He gave the Jade Mirrors

98
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:52,390
to the best talents all over the world

99
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:53,800
and supported them

100
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,270
to gain their help

101
00:03:56,270 --> 00:03:57,390
when he cleaned house.

102
00:03:59,110 --> 00:04:01,080
The Earth Sect is traceless.

103
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:03,920
The Guardians still don't know everything

104
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:06,240
about the Sect Head's demonetization.

105
00:04:07,390 --> 00:04:09,360
He knew you were a Guardian

106
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:10,640
but didn't hide anything.

107
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:13,320
Do you know why?

108
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,080
Are you saying

109
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:20,790
he meant to form an alliance

110
00:04:21,230 --> 00:04:23,320
with you secretly through me?

111
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,280
You'll

112
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:29,350
be the Guardians' spy in the Realm Sect

113
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:32,150
to watch the Earth Sect's every move.

114
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:34,000
Our office

115
00:04:34,470 --> 00:04:36,440
will assist you if necessary.

116
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:37,720
Yes.

117
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:41,080
Have you reached the Qi Stage?

118
00:04:42,790 --> 00:04:43,790
You may begin

119
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,710
learning supreme skills.

120
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:49,030
Li Yuchun'll help you select a manual
from the Sutra Library.

121
00:04:49,590 --> 00:04:51,680
Do you use a saber or a sword?

122
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:52,800
Both are fine.

123
00:04:53,390 --> 00:04:54,230
Saber.

124
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,320
Choose a saber manual

125
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:59,680
that's simple and plain.

126
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:02,440
Ignore the flashy and fancy ones.

127
00:05:02,790 --> 00:05:03,760
Keep in mind.

128
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,470
Fighters,

129
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:07,910
unlike other cultivators,

130
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,830
barely have any super power.

131
00:05:10,030 --> 00:05:11,150
They rely on strength.

132
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:12,160
That's why

133
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:15,080
the simplest is the best.

134
00:05:17,710 --> 00:05:19,760
When you reach even higher stages,

135
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,350
you'll know better.

136
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,030
Thanks for your teaching.

137
00:05:33,220 --> 00:05:35,540
(Sutra Library, Supreme Saber Manual Archive)

138
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,520
You're good.

139
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,880
You went to the Haoqi Tower again.

140
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,790
Lord Wei summoned me.

141
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:46,470
I couldn't say no to him, Chief.

142
00:05:49,230 --> 00:05:50,080
This way, please.

143
00:05:50,230 --> 00:05:51,350
No, I'll show him.

144
00:05:58,200 --> 00:06:01,470
The Manual Archive keeps 407 saber manuals.

145
00:06:03,230 --> 00:06:04,320
They're all here.

146
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:12,470
Are you wondering

147
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:15,560
which one is the strongest?

148
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:19,910
Supreme skills are divided

149
00:06:20,390 --> 00:06:21,390
into techniques

150
00:06:21,790 --> 00:06:22,790
and paths.

151
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:26,000
The latter is out of your league.

152
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:27,440
There are

153
00:06:28,030 --> 00:06:29,200
no strong or weak skills.

154
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:31,200
They depend on you.

155
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,960
This is the saber manual I use.

156
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,860
Would you like to take a look?

157
00:06:38,900 --> 00:06:41,100
(72 Dazzling Skills)
72 Skills?

158
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:43,150
Choose a saber manual

159
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:46,590
that's simple and plain.

160
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:49,760
Ignore the flashy and fancy ones.

161
00:06:53,390 --> 00:06:54,230
Chief,

162
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:56,320
this saber manual

163
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:57,790
is too good.

164
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,270
I'm afraid

165
00:06:59,590 --> 00:07:00,830
I can't handle it.

166
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:03,520
Not just you.

167
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,960
Even I haven't

168
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:08,000
mastered everything in it.

169
00:07:10,590 --> 00:07:12,440
Look around and choose carefully.

170
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:13,720
Yes!

171
00:07:15,790 --> 00:07:17,230
"Fiery Clouds".

172
00:07:18,270 --> 00:07:19,440
There really is such a manual.

173
00:07:19,910 --> 00:07:21,470
"Nine-Dragon Whips"!

174
00:07:21,470 --> 00:07:23,560
Did Nangong Qianrou learn from this manual?

175
00:07:24,910 --> 00:07:28,150
"136 Chops on Mount Huashan".

176
00:07:28,590 --> 00:07:30,880
Why chop it so many times?

177
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,000
Are you torn?

178
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:40,760
Are there new supreme skill manuals?

179
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,230
Saber manuals.

180
00:07:42,230 --> 00:07:44,320
The Bureau sent one over a few days ago

181
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:46,230
and said it'd require a weapon

182
00:07:46,230 --> 00:07:47,560
to unleash the power.

183
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,270
Otherwise, it'd be useless.

184
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,910
A weapon?

185
00:07:51,710 --> 00:07:54,880
That's only for those above the Gold Gongs.

186
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,790
Do you mind fetching it?

187
00:07:56,790 --> 00:07:58,230
I'd like to take a look.

188
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,080
Sure.

189
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:01,140
(One Chop to Kill All)

190
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,960
One Chop?

191
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:11,390
"Nothing in the world can survive this chop.

192
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,440
If there is,

193
00:08:12,590 --> 00:08:14,000
my advice is

194
00:08:14,790 --> 00:08:15,880
run."

195
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,760
Fighters

196
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,320
must not panic in battle.

197
00:08:20,710 --> 00:08:22,230
We can't run away!

198
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:26,270
"Chop once

199
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,910
with a clear conscience.

200
00:08:28,270 --> 00:08:30,120
It can reshape the universe."

201
00:08:33,920 --> 00:08:36,920
Can one really reshape the universe?

202
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,320
Impossible.

203
00:08:39,560 --> 00:08:41,320
Even Duke Zhenbei

204
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:43,280
cannot reshape the universe.

205
00:08:43,680 --> 00:08:45,040
This manual is

206
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,080
(One Chop to Kill All)
a game of bluff.

207
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,680
It's worthless.

208
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,400
It doesn't suit you.

209
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:51,750
Choose something else.

210
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:53,750
But I think

211
00:08:54,110 --> 00:08:55,280
it's perfect.

212
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,440
Do you have a weapon?

213
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,000
No.

214
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,560
But I might get one in the future.

215
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:02,160
I can keep this manual for now.

216
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:05,440
This is your only chance.

217
00:09:06,990 --> 00:09:08,510
Think twice.

218
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:09,800
No need.

219
00:09:10,230 --> 00:09:11,070
I'll take it.

220
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:14,060
(One Chop to Kill All)

221
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:16,320
One Chop to Kill All?

222
00:09:16,870 --> 00:09:17,710
Yes.

223
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:18,680
I told him

224
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:20,440
it'd require a weapon.

225
00:09:20,630 --> 00:09:22,350
Don't waste such a good chance.

226
00:09:22,350 --> 00:09:24,350
But Copper Gong Xu took it anyway.

227
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,110
I see.

228
00:09:27,110 --> 00:09:28,110
You may leave.

229
00:09:31,590 --> 00:09:32,430
What's wrong?

230
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:33,470
Anything else?

231
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:37,280
Hearing that he had to pay 300 liang for it,

232
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,590
he said he didn't bring that much,

233
00:09:38,590 --> 00:09:39,510
and he'd pay later.

234
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:40,710
But given his tone,

235
00:09:40,710 --> 00:09:42,040
I don't think he will.

236
00:09:42,710 --> 00:09:44,470
Deduct it from his salary.

237
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:46,000
Yes.

238
00:09:50,630 --> 00:09:52,110
The Bureau.

239
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,000
Master,

240
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,590
Lord Wei is wise.

241
00:09:55,590 --> 00:09:56,990
After all that we've done,

242
00:09:56,990 --> 00:09:58,710
he must be alerted.

243
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:00,590
It's fine.

244
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:02,160
Anyway,

245
00:10:02,680 --> 00:10:04,080
he'd find out sooner or later.

246
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:06,400
You found out, huh?

247
00:10:08,230 --> 00:10:10,590
It was your order, wasn't it?

248
00:10:10,590 --> 00:10:11,750
I knew

249
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:14,160
the manual came too easily.

250
00:10:15,630 --> 00:10:17,470
When I visited the Bureau earlier,

251
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,230
I told Supervisor

252
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:21,040
to look after you covertly.

253
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:23,830
Although you've found out,

254
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,680
do keep a low profile.

255
00:10:26,470 --> 00:10:27,510
Do not tell others

256
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:29,590
about today's incident.

257
00:10:30,830 --> 00:10:32,440
You aren't their member.

258
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:34,750
Such special treatment might ruin

259
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:36,320
Supervisor's name.

260
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:39,470
Today's incident?

261
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:41,590
What happened today?

262
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:43,640
I...

263
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:45,440
lost my memory.

264
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,710
I don't remember

265
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,120
what happened.

266
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,320
Clever!

267
00:11:02,750 --> 00:11:04,080
You deserve a drink

268
00:11:04,470 --> 00:11:06,080
(Liquor)
for your cleverness.

269
00:11:06,470 --> 00:11:07,310
Sit.

270
00:11:11,830 --> 00:11:12,710
Sit with us, Gang.

271
00:11:12,710 --> 00:11:13,550
Thanks.

272
00:11:14,180 --> 00:11:15,780
(Liquor)

273
00:11:16,350 --> 00:11:19,110
Princess Huaiqing, benevolent

274
00:11:19,110 --> 00:11:21,280
and kind masters like you are rare.

275
00:11:21,510 --> 00:11:22,510
I'm so fortunate

276
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:24,110
to be able to serve you.

277
00:11:24,110 --> 00:11:25,230
Alright.

278
00:11:25,230 --> 00:11:26,470
I'll make toasts.

279
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:28,200
A toast to you, Your Highness.

280
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:30,080
Thank you for cultivating me.

281
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,110
I'll drink up.

282
00:11:35,990 --> 00:11:37,400
Next, I toast you, Gang.

283
00:11:37,870 --> 00:11:40,200
You're above me in terms of seniority.

284
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,320
- Thanks.
- You're humble.

285
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,160
I'll drink up.

286
00:11:49,990 --> 00:11:51,040
Do you mean

287
00:11:51,470 --> 00:11:53,160
you chose me because I appreciated you

288
00:11:53,590 --> 00:11:54,830
