00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:32,120
Rescuing him under the Guardians' noses

578
00:22:32,510 --> 00:22:34,120
is almost impossible.

579
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:35,640
Whoever makes the move,

580
00:22:35,640 --> 00:22:36,840
they'll get into trouble.

581
00:22:37,500 --> 00:22:38,820
(No. 4)

582
00:22:38,820 --> 00:22:40,300
(1, 3, 4, 5, 6)

583
00:22:40,300 --> 00:22:41,780
(No. 3, No. 6)

584
00:22:41,780 --> 00:22:43,820
(1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6)

585
00:22:43,820 --> 00:22:46,100
(No. 3)

586
00:22:46,710 --> 00:22:48,160
I never meant to

587
00:22:48,750 --> 00:22:50,070
trouble all of you.

588
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:52,800
I will

589
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,550
take responsibility

590
00:22:55,600 --> 00:22:56,680
for my actions.

591
00:22:57,740 --> 00:22:59,220
(No. 6)

592
00:23:01,790 --> 00:23:02,630
No. 6,

593
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:03,980
where are you now?

594
00:23:03,980 --> 00:23:07,100
(No. 6)

595
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,310
You guys, go this way.

596
00:23:09,600 --> 00:23:10,440
You two, that way!

597
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:11,300
You guys follow me!

598
00:23:21,550 --> 00:23:22,710
Check every corner.

599
00:23:23,270 --> 00:23:24,990
Leave no stone unturned!

600
00:23:25,120 --> 00:23:25,960
Yes.

601
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:19,960
"A scholar's robe

602
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:21,640
carrying the great spirit

603
00:24:21,640 --> 00:24:23,360
can conceal murderous energy."

604
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:25,600
No. 3 is

605
00:24:26,270 --> 00:24:27,710
from the Yunlu Academy!

606
00:24:32,030 --> 00:24:33,070
(Buddhist Staff?)

607
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:36,440
(He's from Tianyu.)

608
00:24:50,940 --> 00:24:53,780
(Jiang Lyuzhong, Guardian, 4th Rank Fighter)

609
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:54,720
It's odd.

610
00:24:55,840 --> 00:24:57,030
The crimson light is gone.

611
00:24:59,350 --> 00:25:00,630
Song Tingfeng of the Breeze Hall.

612
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:02,160
Zhu Guangxiao of the Breeze Hall.

613
00:25:02,310 --> 00:25:03,750
Greetings, Gold Gong Jiang.

614
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:07,790
Did you find any traces of the killer?

615
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:09,790
We searched the streets.

616
00:25:09,790 --> 00:25:10,710
There's no sign of him.

617
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,880
I found nothing either.

618
00:25:13,710 --> 00:25:14,550
Officers,

619
00:25:14,840 --> 00:25:16,600
was the crimson light here?

620
00:25:16,600 --> 00:25:18,160
Are you questioning us?

621
00:25:18,710 --> 00:25:19,550
I wouldn't dare.

622
00:25:24,310 --> 00:25:25,750
Did you search down there?

623
00:25:29,390 --> 00:25:30,790
Uh... no.

624
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:31,760
No.

625
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:35,710
Are you people of the Breeze Hall

626
00:25:36,510 --> 00:25:38,160
always so reckless?

627
00:25:48,470 --> 00:25:49,310
Mr. Jiang,

628
00:25:49,540 --> 00:25:50,380
we found this.

629
00:25:54,120 --> 00:25:54,960
Chief.

630
00:26:04,550 --> 00:26:05,390
Looks like

631
00:26:05,750 --> 00:26:07,030
some kind of weapon.

632
00:26:11,400 --> 00:26:13,360
Why was it in the ditch?

633
00:26:14,200 --> 00:26:15,840
Did the killer leave it there?

634
00:26:19,880 --> 00:26:20,960
Report it to the high-ups.

635
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:23,040
Yes.

636
00:26:23,230 --> 00:26:24,070
Hold on!

637
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:27,480
Mr. Xu.

638
00:26:28,120 --> 00:26:29,310
It really is him.

639
00:26:29,790 --> 00:26:30,630
Mr. Xu, you haven't

640
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:32,200
gone to the Bureau for a while.

641
00:26:32,200 --> 00:26:33,680
Senior Song keeps bringing you up.

642
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:34,960
Yes, Mr. Xu.

643
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:36,920
Do come for tea when you're free.

644
00:26:36,920 --> 00:26:39,470
We're eager to learn
more alchemy skills from you.

645
00:26:39,710 --> 00:26:40,750
- Alchemy?
- Not today.

646
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:41,920
I'm on duty now.

647
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:43,840
Yes, sure.

648
00:26:47,550 --> 00:26:49,200
Sir, that's my device.

649
00:26:49,990 --> 00:26:50,960
It's yours?

650
00:26:51,550 --> 00:26:53,160
Who are you? Which hall are you in?

651
00:26:53,310 --> 00:26:54,960
He's one of us of the Breeze Hall.

652
00:26:54,960 --> 00:26:56,160
He's Xu Qi'an.

653
00:27:00,510 --> 00:27:02,680
Sir, Lord Wei gave that to me.

654
00:27:03,030 --> 00:27:04,510
May I have it back?

655
00:27:05,360 --> 00:27:06,920
Why was it in the ditch?

656
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:11,710
I had the runs just now.

657
00:27:12,710 --> 00:27:13,960
Perhaps

658
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:15,990
when I relieved myself,

659
00:27:16,310 --> 00:27:17,750
it slipped out.

660
00:27:25,470 --> 00:27:26,550
If you don't believe me,

661
00:27:26,840 --> 00:27:28,270
check with Lord Wei.

662
00:27:31,360 --> 00:27:33,160
You're something else.

663
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:34,000
Yes.

664
00:27:34,010 --> 00:27:34,920
Ignore him.

665
00:27:35,790 --> 00:27:36,630
Officers,

666
00:27:37,230 --> 00:27:38,750
do you know that Guardian

667
00:27:39,030 --> 00:27:39,920
in our office?

668
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:41,750
We know him,

669
00:27:41,920 --> 00:27:43,160
but he might not know us.

670
00:27:45,790 --> 00:27:46,630
How come?

671
00:27:46,990 --> 00:27:48,360
You know Senior Song Qing, right?

672
00:27:48,550 --> 00:27:49,640
Supervisor called him

673
00:27:49,840 --> 00:27:51,880
a once-in-a-century genius in alchemy.

674
00:27:53,070 --> 00:27:54,990
But Senior Song keeps saying this lately.

675
00:27:54,990 --> 00:27:56,200
Do you know what it is?

676
00:27:56,550 --> 00:27:58,030
"Xu Ningyan

677
00:27:58,510 --> 00:28:00,310
is indeed my master."

678
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:05,680
Go to the Breeze Hall tomorrow

679
00:28:06,550 --> 00:28:08,230
and bring him to our hall.

680
00:28:09,230 --> 00:28:10,070
Yes.

681
00:28:11,800 --> 00:28:12,640
Hey, Ningyan,

682
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:13,710
you were amazing.

683
00:28:14,120 --> 00:28:15,990
You won for our hall.

684
00:28:16,340 --> 00:28:17,200
Shut up.

685
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,470
They can still hear us.

686
00:28:18,940 --> 00:28:19,790
So what?

687
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:20,990
We're with Ningyan.

688
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:23,120
What can a mere Gold Gong do to us?

689
00:28:23,510 --> 00:28:24,360
Look at them just now.

690
00:28:26,030 --> 00:28:26,920
"Alchemy!"

691
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:28,270
You're good.

692
00:28:28,470 --> 00:28:29,920
I'm scared. I'm off.

693
00:28:32,790 --> 00:28:34,030
- What's so funny?
- Chief.

694
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:36,070
Stop slacking off.

695
00:28:36,510 --> 00:28:37,350
Go find the killer!

696
00:28:37,510 --> 00:28:38,680
Yes, on it!

697
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:39,880
Stop laughing. Go!

698
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:53,960
No. 3,

699
00:28:55,470 --> 00:28:57,310
why did you send me to a chicken coop?

700
00:29:05,980 --> 00:29:07,220
(South Gate)

701
00:29:11,710 --> 00:29:12,550
Go.

702
00:29:15,300 --> 00:29:16,150
What's on the cart?

703
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,570
- Search it.
- Just some supplies.

704
00:29:18,860 --> 00:29:19,730
We made them.

705
00:29:20,610 --> 00:29:21,450
They're fine.

706
00:29:24,420 --> 00:29:27,060
(Zhang's Plain and Meat Buns)

707
00:29:27,070 --> 00:29:28,160
We looked all night

708
00:29:28,470 --> 00:29:29,310
but found nothing.

709
00:29:29,840 --> 00:29:31,000
We caught two thieves, though.

710
00:29:31,790 --> 00:29:32,640
Not bad.

711
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:34,990
We'll get at least five qian.

712
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:38,030
(How's No. 6 doing now?)

713
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:40,270
We'll go back to report it to Chief.

714
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:41,350
Ningyan,

715
00:29:41,360 --> 00:29:42,230
will you join us?

716
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:44,750
I'm needed elsewhere. Go without me.

717
00:29:44,750 --> 00:29:45,680
See you this afternoon.

718
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,000
That man...

719
00:29:50,270 --> 00:29:51,120
(No. 6!)

720
00:29:52,270 --> 00:29:53,110
What about him?

721
00:29:53,750 --> 00:29:55,360
He's just a scholar, isn't he?

722
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:56,520
No.

723
00:29:56,790 --> 00:29:57,790
He is not.

724
00:29:57,990 --> 00:29:59,070
The robe he's wearing

725
00:29:59,360 --> 00:30:00,310
is someone else's.

726
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:01,600
It doesn't fit at all.

727
00:30:02,440 --> 00:30:03,400
He's walking

728
00:30:03,750 --> 00:30:04,640
with weak steps

729
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:06,070
as if he's out of strength.

730
00:30:06,710 --> 00:30:07,550
Besides,

731
00:30:09,030 --> 00:30:10,270
he came from the Inner City.

732
00:30:11,550 --> 00:30:12,550
Do you mean...?

733
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:19,800
That's right.

734
00:30:20,880 --> 00:30:21,920
He must've gone to the...

735
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:28,960
Imperial Office of Music.

736
00:30:30,790 --> 00:30:31,960
I want to go there, too.

737
00:30:33,030 --> 00:30:34,120
Shall we go there tonight?

738
00:30:36,030 --> 00:30:37,160
I'm exhausted!

739
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:38,020
I want to have fun.

740
00:30:38,030 --> 00:30:39,440
Come on. Go back to rest.

741
00:30:40,790 --> 00:30:42,680
I won't be tired at all in front of girls.

742
00:30:43,020 --> 00:30:46,460
(Breeze Hall)

743
00:31:05,360 --> 00:31:07,440
Look at the time, guys.

744
00:31:07,990 --> 00:31:08,830
Aren't you going to

745
00:31:09,030 --> 00:31:09,990
report it to Chief?

746
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:12,270
Already done.

747
00:31:15,360 --> 00:31:17,750
Why not keep searching for the killer?

748
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:21,200
No rush. We haven't received the order.

749
00:31:25,270 --> 00:31:26,160
How strange.

750
00:31:27,310 --> 00:31:29,120
This is a high-profile case.

751
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,640
It's not strange at all.

752
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:33,600
Earl Pingyuan was a scum anyway.

753
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:35,400
Lord Wei must be glad

754
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:36,640
that pest is dead.

755
00:31:40,310 --> 00:31:41,510
Is that what he's like?

756
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:45,470
Put that away if your peanuts are baked.

757
00:31:45,470 --> 00:31:46,470
It's burning my behind.

758
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:50,840
We searched the area
around Earl Pingyuan's Mansion overnight.

759
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:54,200
There's no sign of the killer in the houses

760
00:31:54,270 --> 00:31:56,070
or the inns in the Inner City.

761
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:57,470
Those in white of the Bureau

762
00:31:57,470 --> 00:31:59,710
didn't sense the murderous energy either.

763
00:31:59,710 --> 00:32:00,880
I'm sorry.

764
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:01,800
Please

765
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:02,920
punish me, Lord Wei.

766
00:32:03,230 --> 00:32:04,840
Look at you, Mr. Jiang.

767
00:32:05,270 --> 00:32:06,960
You let the killer get away

768
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:08,880
even with the Bureau's help.

769
00:32:09,030 --> 00:32:11,880
Do you know those ill-willed court officials

770
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:13,790
are waiting to laugh at our office?

771
00:32:13,990 --> 00:32:15,440
I'll send in more people to search

772
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:16,710
in a wider area.

773
00:32:16,710 --> 00:32:17,600
I promise to

774
00:32:17,600 --> 00:32:18,600
catch the killer

775
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:19,960
before tomorrow.

776
00:32:19,960 --> 00:32:20,800
Relax.

777
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:22,440
You worked all night.

778
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,030
You must be tired.

779
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:26,270
Go back and rest.

780
00:32:30,270 --> 00:32:31,110
Yes.

781
00:32:37,400 --> 00:32:38,550
Lord Wei,

782
00:32:39,070 --> 00:32:42,030
did you give anyone weapons lately?

783
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:46,270
What's your point?

784
00:32:46,270 --> 00:32:49,120
I have something else to report to you.

785
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:56,720
Father,

786
00:32:56,790 --> 00:32:58,070
the Ministry of Justice is

787
00:32:58,270 --> 00:32:59,790
looking for the killer, too, in secret.

788
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:02,070
I think they want to beat us to it

789
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:04,270
and accuse the Guardians of inability.

790
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:06,440
If we couldn't find anything,

791
00:33:06,440 --> 00:33:08,310
what could those losers do?

792
00:33:10,550 --> 00:33:11,470
Lord Wei,

793
00:33:11,470 --> 00:33:12,710
Copper Gong Xu is here.

794
00:33:25,510 --> 00:33:26,880
I have important things to report.

795
00:33:27,360 --> 00:33:28,200
Speak.

796
00:33:31,270 --> 00:33:32,110
Lord Wei,

797
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:34,070
it's sensitive.

798
00:33:34,230 --> 00:33:35,470
Can we speak in private?

799
00:33:36,470 --> 00:33:37,310
What?

800
00:33:37,440 --> 00:33:39,790
Are you, a mere Copper Gong,
asking us to leave?

801
00:33:43,990 --> 00:33:44,840
You may go.

802
00:33:50,120 --> 00:33:51,030
Go.

803
00:33:58,440 --> 00:33:59,440
Come up here.

804
00:34:00,470 --> 00:34:01,310
Yes.

805
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:09,630
Is it about the Realm Sect?

806
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:13,030
It's about Earl Pingyuan.

807
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:16,920
The one who killed him

808
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:18,880
is No. 6 of the Realm Sect.

809
00:34:20,990 --> 00:34:21,840
The motive?

810
00:34:28,670 --> 00:34:30,030
Letting a killer go

811
00:34:30,320 --> 00:34:31,840
is as guilty as murder!

812
00:34:32,240 --> 00:34:33,240
Are you insane?

813
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,400
I'm sorry.

814
00:34:36,670 --> 00:34:38,360
I'm guilty beyond forgiveness.

815
00:34:38,550 --> 00:34:39,880
I struggled overnight but couldn't

816
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:41,840
live with a guilty conscience.

817
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:43,190
I have to tell you the truth.

818
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:44,440
However you'll punish me,

819
00:34:44,510 --> 00:34:45,630
I'll accept it.

820
00:34:56,670 --> 00:34:57,840
Earlier today,

821
00:34:58,440 --> 00:34:59,840
when I chatted with others,

822
00:35:00,590 --> 00:35:01,590
I learned

823
00:35:02,240 --> 00:35:03,760
that you were rebuked by His Majesty.

824
00:35:04,510 --> 00:35:06,470
Other court officials ganged up on you

825
00:35:06,550 --> 00:35:07,720
to bring you down.

826
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:10,990
I owe you more than I can repay.

827
00:35:10,990 --> 00:35:12,030
- I...
- Enough.

828
00:35:13,190 --> 00:35:14,400
You don't

829
00:35:14,590 --> 00:35:15,720
owe me.

830
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:18,960
Get to the point.

831
00:35:24,110 --> 00:35:26,510
Earl Pingyuan secretly supported traffickers

832
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,400
to sell people

833
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:29,590
to rake in money!

834
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:32,280
They sold children and women

835
00:35:32,720 --> 00:35:34,720
to brothels and sweatshops.

836
00:35:34,990 --> 00:35:36,070
They became thieves

837
00:35:36,470 --> 00:35:38,800
and even lost their limbs
to satisfy others' fetishes.

838
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:41,470
Hearing such inhumanity,

839
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:44,190
I'd rather kill those animals myself.

840
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:52,920
Get up.

841
00:35:57,670 --> 00:35:58,510
Yes.

842
00:36:03,400 --> 00:36:04,320
Xu Qi'an,

843
00:36:06,550 --> 00:36:08,030
how well do you know

844
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:09,630
the Realm Sect?

845
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:13,440
How well do you know Jinlian

846
00:36:13,960 --> 00:36:14,920
of the Earth Sect?

847
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:21,470
Investigation shows

848
00:36:21,840 --> 00:36:24,920
the Earl did keep a group of traffickers.

849
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:27,110
But did No. 6

850
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:29,550
kill him for his junior fellow

851
00:36:30,150 --> 00:36:31,840
without any hidden agenda?

852
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:34,510
Maybe

853
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:37,440
the Earl was involved in other things, too.

854
00:36:38,670 --> 00:36:39,720
Maybe

855
00:36:41,150 --> 00:36:43,990
those traffickers did something else

856
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:46,240
that led to their doom.

857
00:36:47,990 --> 00:36:49,510
Did you consider

858
00:36:50,670 --> 00:36:52,030
all those possibilities?

859
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,360
(He's teaching me.)

860
00:36:56,880 --> 00:36:58,190
(He's helping me grow.)

861
00:36:59,030 --> 00:37:00,240
I was reckless.

862
00:37:00,670 --> 00:37:01,510
Never mind.

863
00:37:01,510 --> 00:37:02,550
You stay

864
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:04,760
out of this case.

865
00:37:05,240 --> 00:37:07,150
I'll assign it to others.

866
00:37:07,720 --> 00:37:09,550
Keep your cover in the Realm Sect.

867
00:37:10,150 --> 00:37:11,110
Your priority

868
00:37:11,110 --> 00:37:12,280
is to check out

869
00:37:12,510 --> 00:37:14,920
the identity of everyone there.

870
00:37:15,760 --> 00:37:16,600
And...

871
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:24,280
Stay safe.

872
00:37:31,190 --> 00:37:32,670
I'll give it my all, sir.

873
00:37:37,180 --> 00:37:38,100
(Peace)

874
00:37:38,100 --> 00:37:39,240
That's absurd!

875
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:41,070
You're a Gold Gong.

876
