906
00:39:24,720 --> 00:39:25,800
but wouldn't dare ask.

907
00:39:27,190 --> 00:39:28,140
Thanks for your concern.

908
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:30,590
I'm safe for now.

909
00:39:30,990 --> 00:39:32,370
(No. 6)
So

910
