did No. 3 help you out?

911
00:39:34,400 --> 00:39:35,240
Yes.

912
00:39:36,190 --> 00:39:37,320
Thanks to him,

913
00:39:38,190 --> 00:39:39,400
I made it out.

914
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:41,660
(No. 3)

915
00:39:42,150 --> 00:39:44,190
Where is No. 3?

916
00:39:44,400 --> 00:39:45,470
Is he in trouble?

917
00:39:45,720 --> 00:39:47,590
He's blessed by the heavens.

918
00:39:48,110 --> 00:39:49,070
I'm sure he's fine.

919
00:39:49,070 --> 00:39:50,660
(No. 3)

920
00:39:51,630 --> 00:39:53,030
- No. 3!
- No. 6.

921
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:54,240
I heard the news.

922
00:39:54,500 --> 00:39:56,550
(No. 6, No. 4, No. 2)
My office got anonymous tips.

923
00:39:56,550 --> 00:39:57,760
They'll keep going after you.

924
00:39:57,760 --> 00:39:58,630
Be prepared

925
00:39:58,630 --> 00:39:59,550
and stay alert.

926
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:01,800
Thanks for the heads-up.

927
00:40:03,400 --> 00:40:05,320
No. 3 has helped No. 6 out

928
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:07,070
and infiltrated into the Guardians.

929
00:40:07,630 --> 00:40:09,510
I knew he was capable.

930
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:11,630
No. 6, now that No. 3 is here,

931
00:40:11,630 --> 00:40:13,840
can you tell us how you got out?

932
00:40:15,800 --> 00:40:16,640
No. 3,

933
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,240
