934
00:40:19,510 --> 00:40:20,350
I say it?

935
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:22,320
Why not?

936
00:40:22,400 --> 00:40:23,760
I have nothing to hide.

937
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:24,760
Go ahead.

938
00:40:24,990 --> 00:40:25,830
Sure.

939
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:27,240
Here's the thing.

940
00:40:27,880 --> 00:40:28,720
No. 3

941
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:30,590
gave me a scholar's robe

942
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:33,110
to conceal my murderous energy.

943
00:40:33,110 --> 00:40:33,990
Yes.

944
00:40:34,510 --> 00:40:36,800
But that wasn't enough.

945
00:40:37,030 --> 00:40:40,470
Then I brought him to an inn that no one knew

946
00:40:40,470 --> 00:40:41,360
to hide.

947
00:40:42,550 --> 00:40:43,670
Even so,

948
00:40:43,910 --> 00:40:45,610
