the Guardians were everywhere.

949
00:40:45,740 --> 00:40:47,350
How did you hide from them?

950
00:40:47,630 --> 00:40:49,190
He couldn't.

951
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:52,880
After a while, they found traces of him.

952
00:40:53,320 --> 00:40:54,800
Thanks to my Plan B,

953
00:40:54,960 --> 00:40:56,880
he made a narrow escape.

954
00:40:56,990 --> 00:40:57,880
What did you do?

955
00:40:58,920 --> 00:41:00,960
I put on the robe I had got

956
00:41:01,070 --> 00:41:02,030
from No. 6

957
00:41:02,190 --> 00:41:03,360
and jumped out of the window,

958
00:41:03,470 --> 00:41:05,760
drawing the attention of the Guardians

959
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:07,070
and those of the Bureau to me.

960
00:41:07,470 --> 00:41:09,590
