963
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:13,400
Am I right,

964
00:41:13,670 --> 00:41:14,840
No. 6?

965
00:41:19,670 --> 00:41:20,590
Yes,

966
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:21,990
I guess.

967
00:41:25,150 --> 00:41:27,670
